The paper deals with parameterized queries on databases, which is a core topic in the field of database management (cs.DB). The use of binding patterns and execution plans also involves concepts from artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and deep learning (cs.DL). The paper also discusses the use of the method in real-world web services, which falls under software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL).
